==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Moderato
<hw>Mod`e*ra"to</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a. & adv.</pos> <ety>[It.
See <er>Moderate</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>With a moderate
degree of quickness; moderately.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Allegro moderato</b></col>, <cd>a little slower than
allegro.</cd> -- <col><b>Andante moderato</b></col>, <cd>a little faster
than andante.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moderator</ent>⟦br⟧
